name: Star wars
tagline: Computer graphics scene developed with OpenGL Shading Language and C ++.
body:
### Star Wars Project
This is an open project on Star Wars. It is being developed in C ++ with OpenGL. All 3D models were taken from the internet and are freely accessible.
